text
@d1 16
a16 26
---+ BioCASE Protocol

Homepage: http://www.biocase.org/products/protocols/index.shtml

Currently implemented version 1.3 of the BioCASE protocol:
XML Schema: http://www.bgbm.org/biodivinf/Schema/protocol_1_3.xsd

----

---+++ Suggested improved BioCASE protocol version 2

It includes :
   * a metadata request type
   * allows to specify parts of an existing schema to be returned only ("partial search")
   * allows to freely specify the structure of returned data ("flexible search")
   * ...

XML Schema: http://www.bgbm.org/biodivinf/Schema/protocol_proposal_2.0/protocol_2_0.xsd

---++++ Examples

   * Full Search [[http://www.bgbm.org/biodivinf/Schema/protocol_proposal_2.0/request_full.xml][request]]
   * Partial Search [[http://www.bgbm.org/biodivinf/Schema/protocol_proposal_2.0/request_partial.xml][request]]/[[http://www.bgbm.org/biodivinf/Schema/protocol_proposal_2.0/response_partial.xml][response]]
   * Custom Search [[http://www.bgbm.org/biodivinf/Schema/protocol_proposal_2.0/request_structured.xml][request]]/[[http://www.bgbm.org/biodivinf/Schema/protocol_proposal_2.0/response_structured.xml][response]]


@


